<h3>What to Avoid as a Rep</h3>

<p>Tools with <code>Requires Admin</code> or <code>Enterprise Grade</code> tags are not built for individual use. Clay ($149/month, requires RevOps setup), Gong (custom pricing, requires admin), Outreach (custom pricing, requires IT), and ZoomInfo (custom pricing, requires procurement) are all tools that your company buys for you &mdash; not tools you buy for yourself.</p>

